---

## Project-Agnostic vs Specific

**Project-Agnostic Skills** (portable):
- `ship` - Works in any git project
- `sync` - Works in any multi-branch project
- `commit` - Works anywhere
- `advisor` - Works with any CLAUDE.md
- `memory` - Works with any Supabase

**Project-Specific Skills**:
- Custom integrations tied to your specific setup
- Skills referencing hardcoded channels or endpoints

